com.example.lunchmeet.lunchmeet

Class Group

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.lunchmeet.lunchmeet.Group

  • public class Group
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to keep track of formed lunch group information, such as the members, capacity, and current size of a group. Includes methods to add and remove members from a group, as well as getters and setters for the group information.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Group(User user)
      Default constructor that creates a group of maximum 6 members.
      Group(User user, int c)
      Parametrized constructor that creates a group with capacity set by the group creator.
